title: Magician from Another World
summary: Magician from Another World ManhuaThe MC, Zhang Daoling, who had obtained the treasure and qualitfications to ascend to immortal, was set up and died along with his lover, Xianger. However, Zhang Daoling and Xianger were reincarnated in a different world. Zhang Daoling vowed to reach his peak, find Xianger, and return to his previous world to take revenge.
